//sfdx: Turn on Apex debug Log for Replay Debugger

//sfdx: get apex debug logs
inside sfdx/tools/Debug

inside class select the file
set a breakpoint, click and click inside log, launch apex debugger with the current file

from top left add configuration
select Apex log debugger. // as your environment

adds launch configuration at launch.json

clicking on launch apex debugger at top left again




